history.proof: intros OrtX LeX. qsimpl time: 1 use: lb_ortho_meet_nil. qsimpl time: 1 use: lb_ortho_meet_nil,lb_mask_equiv_rst_Transitive. qsimpl time: 1 use: lb_ortho_sym,lb_ortho_meet_nil,lb_mask_equiv_rst_Transitive. apply lb_mask_meet. qsimpl time: 1 use: lb_mask_le_iff,lb_ortho_sym,lb_ortho_meet_nil,lb_mask_equiv_rst_Transitive. apply lb_mask_equiv_rst_Symmetric. hauto lq: on use: lb_ortho_anti_left, lb_meet_join_idem, lb_meet_dec_left, lb_join_right, lb_mask_meet, lb_meet_comm, lb_join_comm, lb_mask_equiv_refl unfold: lb_mask_equiv.

exceptions.exn: In environment a, x : lb OrtX : a ⟂ x LeX : x ⪯ a H : forall x y : lb, x ⟂ y -> x ↓ y ≂ nil H0 : forall x y : lb, x ⟂ y -> x ↓ y ⪯ nil Unable to unify "?M1492 ↓ ?M1493 ⪯ nil" with "x ⪯ nil /\\ nil ⪯ x".

In environment a, x : lb OrtX : a ⟂ x LeX : x ⪯ a H : forall x y : lb, x ↓ y ≂ nil -> x ⟂ y H0 : forall x y : lb, x ⟂ y -> x ↓ y ≂ nil H1 : forall x y z : lb, x ≂ y -> y ≂ z -> x ⪯ z Unable to unify "?M2398 ⪯ x" with "x ⪯ nil".

In environment H2 : Transitive lb_mask_equiv a, x : lb OrtX : a ⟂ x LeX : x ⪯ a H : forall x y : lb, x ↓ y ≂ nil -> x ⟂ y H0 : forall x y : lb, x ⟂ y -> x ↓ y ≂ nil Unable to unify "?M3013 ⟂ ?M3012" with "x ⪯ nil".

In environment H4 : Transitive lb_mask_equiv H1 : forall a b : lb, a ⟂ b -> b ⟂ a a, x : lb OrtX : a ⟂ x LeX : x ⪯ a H : forall x y : lb, x ↓ y ≂ nil -> x ⟂ y H0 : forall x y : lb, x ⟂ y -> x ↓ y ≂ nil H2 : forall x y : lb, x ≂ y -> forall x0 y0 : lb, x0 ≂ y0 -> x ⪯ x0 -> y ⪯ y0 Unable to unify "?M3716 ⪯ ?M3719" with "x ↓ nil ⪯ x /\\ x ⪯ x ↓ nil".

original: intros OrtX LeX. apply lb_ortho_meet_nil. apply lb_mask_equiv_rst_Transitive with (z := x). - apply lb_ortho_sym. apply lb_mask_meet. auto. - apply lb_mask_le_iff. apply lb_mask_equiv_rst_Symmetric. auto. auto.
